Melissa,Data,creates,data,quality,and,address,management,solutions,for,websites,and,businesses,Their,services,standardize,verify,and,enhance,global,contact,data,including,addresses,phone,numbers,and,email,addresses,The,Melissa,Data,RightFielder,Object,API,allows,customer,applications,to,turn,unformatted,contact,information,into,structured,data,Capable,of,handling,name,address,phone,and,email,text,the,API,uses,two,parsing,engines,to,identify,extract,and,organize,data,whether,that,input,data,is,formatted,or,freeform